{"data":{"post":{"id":"f7016fa5-6bea-5cb3-8bdf-c2e611d15cd9","html":"<p>感谢贝妈提供照片(馒头蛋糕)                 </p>\n<p>媒体的力量很强大，从“虎爸虎妈”到“牛蛙计划”，让全民都在关注教育。<br>\n<br>\n如果你是父母，你会怎样对待孩子的学习？<br>\n如果你是孩子，你会怎样面对考试与父母的态度？<br>\n如果你是老师，你会为学生们构造一个什么样的“场”？竞赛场？探索场？……<br>\n</p>\n<h4>故事1:馒头生日蛋糕</h4>\n<p>贝贝快过5岁生日，由于近期表现不够好，得到的小星星不够多，加上贝贝感冒咳嗽，贝妈不太想给他买奶油生日蛋糕。<br>\n贝妈：贝贝，最近这个月的小星星换不到生日蛋糕，要不，我们自己动手做馒头生日蛋糕。<br>\n贝贝：好啊，好啊，做馒头生日蛋糕。我还想做章鱼型的馒头……<br>\n<br>\n章鱼型馒头初型,还有玫瑰花馒头、小猪猪馒头、还有磨牙棒……<br>\n<figure><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/9eb9b/cake1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 540px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"cake1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/9eb9b/cake1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/131ba/cake1.jpg 200w,\n/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/62ad2/cake1.jpg 400w,\n/static/279645d536c16170121ffadff0e63374/9eb9b/cake1.jpg 540w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    <figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">unsplash.com</figcaption></figure>\n<figure>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/964c815b8bfbb2a8ac9b5d5a46aba751/9eb9b/rose.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 540px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"rose\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/964c815b8bfbb2a8ac9b5d5a46aba751/9eb9b/rose.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/964c815b8bfbb2a8ac9b5d5a46aba751/131ba/rose.jpg 200w,\n/static/964c815b8bfbb2a8ac9b5d5a46aba751/62ad2/rose.jpg 400w,\n/static/964c815b8bfbb2a8ac9b5d5a46aba751/9eb9b/rose.jpg 540w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    <figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">unsplash.com</figcaption></figure>\n<figure>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d3936616f0823f66d761da6dbcfe8546/9eb9b/pig.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 540px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"pig\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d3936616f0823f66d761da6dbcfe8546/9eb9b/pig.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d3936616f0823f66d761da6dbcfe8546/131ba/pig.jpg 200w,\n/static/d3936616f0823f66d761da6dbcfe8546/62ad2/pig.jpg 400w,\n/static/d3936616f0823f66d761da6dbcfe8546/9eb9b/pig.jpg 540w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    <figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">unsplash.com</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>馒头出炉了，有没有垂涎若滴的感觉，o(∩_∩)o 哈哈      </p>\n<p><figure>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/be40eb78d5c2b1c6ab67e7da771d6141/925b4/whole_picture.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 150%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"whole picture\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/be40eb78d5c2b1c6ab67e7da771d6141/925b4/whole_picture.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/be40eb78d5c2b1c6ab67e7da771d6141/b9875/whole_picture.jpg 200w,\n/static/be40eb78d5c2b1c6ab67e7da771d6141/21597/whole_picture.jpg 400w,\n/static/be40eb78d5c2b1c6ab67e7da771d6141/925b4/whole_picture.jpg 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    <figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">unsplash.com</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>贝妈：贝贝，你以后上小学了，自己好好学习，回家妈妈就给你做好吃的，好不好？<br>\n贝妈继续补充，你读初中、高中、大学、研究生，都自己好好学习，回家妈妈就给你做好吃的，怎么样？<br>\n贝贝：好啊，好啊。<br>\n<br>\n<em>片刻过后</em>   </p>\n<h4>故事2:白纸黑字 —— 写下来</h4>\n<p>贝贝：妈妈，你用笔写下来哈<br>\n贝妈：写什么？<br>\n贝贝：你以后经常给我做好吃的啊。<br>\n贝妈：哈哈哈……前面那句，自己搞定学习……<br>\n</p>","fields":{"slug":"/study-hard-delicious-food/","prefix":"2018-11-04"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Study and food","author":"文:Jane 图(馒头蛋糕):贝妈","category":"funny","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/be40eb78d5c2b1c6ab67e7da771d6141/ada8c/whole_picture.jpg"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"e6ec6ad4-4c6b-586c-bfdf-8cdf2d09548f","html":"<p>hustlrb<br>\n<br>\n明德厚学 求是创新</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/study-hard-delicious-food/","prev":{"id":"914b5542-fb69-5024-821a-2a5861d16501","fields":{"slug":"/how-to-introduce-yourself/","prefix":"2018-10-31","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How to introduce yourself ?","category":"funny"}},"next":{"id":"8a77e266-35d1-556c-822b-16d501e21c43","fields":{"slug":"/rice-noodles/","prefix":"2018-11-08","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"你是否记得，多久学会使用筷子吃东西？","category":"funny"}},"source":"posts"}}